	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas tuae pietatis binas accepi, frater charissime, priores scriptas iunii 7., posteriores 1. iulii et in his literas d. consulis <persName ref="p3927" cert="high">Welseri</persName>, quas hic remitto.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Exulcerata sunt ubique omnia, bellis et proditionibus scatent omnia, quia totus hic mundus positus est in malo et bona parte sciens et volens veritatem oppugnat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="auto_name">Italia</placeName> misere laceratur fame et bello, non desinit interim italiscere; omnia per Germaniam metu belli trepidant; sed non desinimus germanizare; iusta ergo sunt dei iudicia.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid, quod ministri postergata omni mansuetudine instar rebidarum belluarum furiunt et ferociunt in fratres?</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <persName type="auto_name">Lutheranis</persName> loquor; mirum est, quam insaniant isti contra nos.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Varii hic sparguntur rumores de rebus variis; certum esse aiunt <placeName type="auto_name">Poloniam</placeName> recepisse Christi evangelium; in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> exercetur carnificina truculentissima.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Deus adsit nobis!</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentinae</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l410" cert="high">Regenspurgi</placeName> et in aliis imperii urbibus nihil nunc habent, quod Lutherani in tanta omnium corruptione insectentur quam nos.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oremus dominum, ut afflictae adsit ecclesiae; certum est Lutheranos papistis esse nobis infensiores longe.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Alterum ex hisce libellis tibi servabis, alterum dabis d. consuli <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1057" cert="high">Fuchsio</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName ref="p1057" cert="high">Peter Fuchs</persName>.</note>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam <persName type="auto_name">Samuel Wittenbachius</persName> multorum calamitatibus praemonitus iam abstineat a milicia, quae paratur modo!</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutabis illum et hortaberis, sui et suorum meminerit.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutabis inprimis d. consulem, d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4868" cert="high">Iacobum Funklium</persName>, d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p5101" cert="high">Valerium</persName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p5101" cert="high">Göuffi</persName>.</note> et reliquos amicos.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vive et vale una cum omni tua familia.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tiguri</placeName> 21. iulii 1555.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullingerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="de" type="auto">An herren <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Johansen Hallern</persName>, minen lieben gevattern, disen brieff gen <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l49" cert="high">Byel</placeName> zuͦ fertigen an den erwirdigen m. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosien Blaureren</persName>, predicanten zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l49" cert="high">Byel</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
